author: Henry David Thoreau
message: I cannot make my days longer so I strive to make them better.

message: Tension is who you think you should be. Relaxation is who you are.

author: Helen Keller
message: Never bend your head. Always hold it high. Look the world right in the eye.

author: Albert Schweitzer
